name: Tenant Expiry Email to Roker Power Admin User
template:
Hello {RokerAdministratorName},

This is a system-generated email notification regarding a tenant user account – {TenantName}, will be expired on {ExpiryDate}.

If you wish to extend the access for the tenant, you can {LoginUrl} to the Roker account and update the expiry date for the tenant’s account. 

Thank you!
